on Martyrdom: Cannot claim a specific person is a martyr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-\u2018Ajfa reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou say about those who are killed or died in your campaigns that \u2018this person was killed as a martyr\u2019 or \u2018this person died as a martyr.\u2019 Perhaps he only intended to load his animal with spoils,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32734,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/11\/seven-martyrs-besides-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":3225,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Seven types of martyrdom besides fighting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn \u2018Atik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are seven martyrs besides one who is killed in the way of Allah: the victim of plague is a martyr, the one who drowns is a martyr, the one who dies of chest pain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14061,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/08\/who-is-a-martyr\/","url_meta":{"origin":3225,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Martyrs: Who do you consider your martyrs?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, s